WEBVTT

00:00:01.451 --> 00:00:04.553
I am an ideas activist.

00:00:06.075 --> 00:00:10.422
That means I fight
for ideas I believe in

00:00:11.406 --> 00:00:13.748
to have their place in the sun,

00:00:13.772 --> 00:00:18.304
regardless of which side
of the equator they were born.

00:00:18.946 --> 00:00:20.345
As well I should.

00:00:20.369 --> 00:00:22.809
I myself am from that part of the world

00:00:22.833 --> 00:00:26.881
often euphemistically referred to
as either "the Global South"

00:00:26.905 --> 00:00:28.316
or "the developing world."

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:30.269
But let's be blunt about it: